OL,3,CSAS had 'golden pass to get away with
OL,4,Cmurder' in Afghanistan, inquiry told
OL,6,FA former special forces officer has
OL,7,Ftold a public inquiry that they had a
OL,8,F"golden pass... to get away with
OL,9,Fmurder" in Afghanistan.
OL,11,FThe witness is one of the former
OL,12,Fmembers of the SAS who are giving
OL,13,Fevidence about alleged murders in the
OL,14,Fwar-torn nation between 2010 and 2013
OL,15,Fin a series of closed hearings, as
OL,16,Fpart of the Afghanistan inquiry.
