OL,3,CSAS had 'golden pass to get away with
OL,4,Cmurder' in Afghanistan, inquiry told
OL,6,FAnother witness - known only as N1799
OL,7,F- said that he learnt of alleged war
OL,8,Fcrimes while training with someone
OL,9,Ffrom a different unit, referred to as
OL,10,FUKSF1.
OL,12,FHe told the probe that the accusations
OL,13,Fcontradicted a talk previously given
OL,14,Fby commanding officers which stated
OL,15,F"UK special forces does not operate
OL,16,Foutside of the law".
OL,18,FThe witness told the inquiry that the
OL,19,Fconversations with the other officer
OL,20,Fwere "graphic".
