OL,3,CSAS had 'golden pass to get away with
OL,4,Cmurder' in Afghanistan, inquiry told
OL,6,FA witness, known as N2107, told the
OL,7,Finquiry that they regret not reporting
OL,8,Fconcerns about extrajudicial killings
OL,9,Fin the country.
OL,11,FDocuments show that the officer
OL,12,Fbelieved by April 2011 that the unit
OL,13,Fmay have been committing killings
OL,14,Fwithout the sanction of any judicial
OL,15,For legal process.
OL,17,FThe officer expressed the concerns in
OL,18,Femails to friends and colleagues after
OL,19,FJanuary 2011, but did not report this
OL,20,Fto the Royal Military Police.
