OL,9,Fwere being "treated like dogs" by
OL,10,FUKSF1.
OL,12,FFormer Defence Secretary Sir Ben
OL,13,FWallace told BBC Radio 4 Today
OL,14,Fprogramme: "Let's not forget our
OL,15,Fspecial forces personnel go where no-
OL,16,Fone else can go, they do things in the
OL,17,Fhighest environment of danger in order
OL,18,Fto protect this country and its
OL,19,Fcitizens ` they are exceptional people.
