OL,6,FA number of investigations have looked
OL,7,Finto the forces' behaviour.
OL,9,FNo charges were brought under
OL,10,FOperation Northmoor, which was set up
OL,11,Fin 2014 to examine allegations of
OL,12,Fexecutions by special forces,
OL,13,Fincluding those of children.
OL,15,FA further investigation, codenamed
OL,16,FOperation Cestro, saw three soldiers
OL,17,Freferred to the Service Prosecuting
OL,18,FAuthority, but none of them were
OL,19,Fprosecuted.
OL,21,FThe Afghanistan inquiry continues.
